{
  "texts": [
    "The current experiments are conducted exclusively on the commonsense QA and household datasets.",
    "However, our approach is also applicable to a broader range of fields including medical (Tang et al., 2023), arithmetic (Cobbe et al., 2021), web browsing (Xie et al., 2023), and embodied agents (Yang et al., 2023).",
    "This suggests a potential for wider applicability that has yet to be explored.",
    "-Agent Systems.",
    "Presently, our research focuses on the application of single agents."
  ]
}